         <abstract>
            <p>The key to eliminating the exchange specialist is a new kind of limit order--the independent limit order--that permits the ordinary investor to help make the market. Through the proper combination of independent limit orders and market orders, he can achieve almost any desired balance between the cost of trading and the time required to complete the trade.</p>
